verbose_text: Where CiAlx : initial root length measured before exposure to the nutrient solution at an " x " level of Al; CfAlx : final root length measured after n days of exposure to the nutrient solution at an " x " level of Al; CiAl 0 : initial root length before exposure to the solution without any Al; and CfAl 0 : final root length measured after n days of exposure to the nutrient solution without Al.
